Package: icmBenchmarkR
Title: Automated ICM Training Quality Benchmarking Reports
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given   = "Nick",
           family  = "Plummer", 
           email   ="nickplummer@nhs.net",
           role    = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1239-9253"))
Description: Tools to import ICM training quality assessments from M365 Forms,
    clean and summarise data, and generate hospital-level benchmarking
    reports via R Markdown templates. Designed for regional or national rollout,
    including support for Shiny interface.
